## Update Spyder
Anaconda Prompt
$ conda update spyder

## Update Jupyter Notebook
Anaconda Prompt
$ conda update jupyter

## Update Anaconda
Anaconda Prompt
$ conda update conda
$ conda update --all [allow 15 minutes]

## Update Python
Anaconda Prompt
Update python
$ conda update python

## Update Anaconda
conda update conda
conda update anaconda

